This project is an Unmanned Aerial System with Smart Surveillance for SAR missons and Disaster response
It's based on Arduino MCUs
The communication between the UAV and the remote control is done via NRF24L01 communication module

Note:

The Servo motors are connected as follows: 
Right Flap: 2
Left FLap: 3
Right Rudder: 4
Left Rudder: 5
Throttle: 7

NRF24L01 connections: 

CE: 9
CSN: 10
MOSI: 11
MISO: 12
SCK: 13
Vcc: 3.3V
GND: GND
